Property and Casualty Application for Vlocity Insurance Application Suite

Configure Rating Engine for Property using Expression Sets
The rating engine for Homeowners (HO3) and Renters (HO4) products is reconfigured to work with expression sets and decision matrices.
Enhanced Quote User Interface for Commercial Products
We've updated the quote user interface for commercial products which allows you to edit coverages and insured Items at a more granular level.
Enhanced User Experience for Auto FNOL OmniScript
We've updated the Multi-Auto FNOL OmniScript using our OmniStudio FlexCard capabilities to deliver an enhanced user experience.
